      <title>检察官称托克集团“狼在守护羊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/the-wolves-were-guarding-the-sheep-at-trafigura-says-prosecutor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士检察官表示，托克集团的反腐败控制措施因高管控制其合规委员会而受到损害，他们要求对前首席运营官迈克·温赖特 (Mike Wainwright) 判处四年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/the-wolves-were-guarding-the-sheep-at-trafigura-says-prosecutor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:59:26 GMT</pubDate>
