    <item>
      <title>Balbec 与高盛合作发行 8 亿欧元西班牙抵押贷款债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/balbec-taps-goldman-for-800-million-spanish-mortgage-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，另类资产管理公司 Balbec Capital LP 已聘请高盛集团公司 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 将其过去几年在西班牙购买的贷款捆绑在一起，发行首批西班牙证券化产品，总额约 8 亿欧元（8.46 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/balbec-taps-goldman-for-800-million-spanish-mortgage-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gallagher 同意以 130 亿美元收购 AssuredPartners</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/gallagher-agrees-to-buy-assuredpartners-in-13-45-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Arthur J. Gallagher &amp; Co 同意以 134.5 亿美元收购保险经纪公司 AssuredPartners，这是其有史以来规模最大的一笔收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/gallagher-agrees-to-buy-assuredpartners-in-13-45-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿滋国际考虑收购美国巧克力制造商好时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，零食和糖果公司亿滋国际 (Mondelez International Inc.) 正在探索收购美国标志性巧克力制造商好时公司 (Hershey Co.)，这笔交易可能打造出一家总销售额近 500 亿美元的食品巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦电力用户为太阳能计划筹集 2.5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/zimbabwe-power-users-raise-250-million-for-floating-solar-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的工业电力用户已从非洲进出口银行获得 2.5 亿美元，用于在世界上最大的人工湖上建造浮动太阳能电池板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/zimbabwe-power-users-raise-250-million-for-floating-solar-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:56:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
